=== friend_introduction.glp ===
Friend-mediated introduction protocol.
Goal: social_graph(Id, [msg(user, Id, introduce(P, Q))|In], Fs)

When agent r is friends with both p and q, r introduces them.
Three-party protocol with attestation exchange:
1. r creates channel pair
2. r sends intro to both p and q
3. Recipients exchange attestations
4. User consulted for final decision
